{"id": "lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MTE2OQ_0009", "text": "昨日爲你衝過綠茶 哀痛痊癒了吧", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 2, 5, 3, 4, 2, 0, 3, 4, 0, 2, 5, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zok3", "jat6", "nei5", "cung1", "gwo3", "luk6", "caa4", "oi1", "tung3", "cyun4", "jyu6", "liu5", "baa6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "昨日", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "爲", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "衝過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "綠茶", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "哀痛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "痊癒", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "了", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吧", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "寧靜雪", "artists": ["張信哲"], "lyricists": ["林若寧"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1169", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MTE2OQ_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MTE2OQ_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MTE2OQ_0010", "text": "前塵暖 如何短 同行觀賞一次八月雪", "structure": {"line_index": 10, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 5, 0, 0, 9, 0, 0, 3, 9, 3, 4, 4, 2, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["cin4", "can4", "nyun5", "jyu4", "ho4", "dyun2", "tung4", "hang4", "gun1", "soeng2", "jat1", "ci3", "baat3", "jyut6", "syut3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "前塵", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "暖", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "如何", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "短", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "同行", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "觀賞", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一次", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "八月", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "雪", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "寧靜雪", "artists": ["張信哲"], "lyricists": ["林若寧"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1169", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MTE2OQ_0009", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MTE2OQ_0011", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MTE2OQ_0011", "text": "我很好 不要牽掛 記得嗎", "structure": {"line_index": 11, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 9, 9, 3, 4, 3, 4, 4, 3, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "han2", "hou2", "bat1", "jiu3", "hin1", "gwaa3", "gei3", "dak1", "maa1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "很", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "好", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "牽掛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "記得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "嗎", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "寧靜雪", "artists": ["張信哲"], "lyricists": ["林若寧"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1169", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MTE2OQ_0010", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MTE2OQ_0012", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MTE2OQ_0012", "text": "獨個於冰封的故園 一聲聲咳嗽也極幽怨", "structure": {"line_index": 12, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 3, 3, 3, 3, 4, 0, 3, 3, 3, 3, 4, 5, 2, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["duk6", "go3", "jyu1", "bing1", "fung1", "dik1", "gu3", "jyun4", "jat1", "sing1", "sing1", "kat1", "sau3", "jaa5", "gik6", "jau1", "jyun3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "獨個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "於", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "冰封", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "故園", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一聲聲", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "咳嗽", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "極", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "幽怨", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "寧靜雪", "artists": ["張信哲"], "lyricists": ["林若寧"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1169", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MTE2OQ_0011", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MTE2OQ_0013", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
